Complete desktop environment using ncurses based apps.

Changes include:
 - mutt patch providing ability to disable IMAP authentication using SASL;
 - mutt patch preventing segfault when using imap;
 - mutt sidebar patch for proper line length calculation (it assumes utf8 locale);
 - screen vertical split patch;
 - mcabber-modules ebuild;
 - mod-mcabber-pep ebuild;
 - mod-mcabber-avatar ebuild;
 - loudmouth patch for proper handling of incorrect UTF-8 sequences
